---
title: Pan-Fried Salmon and Soy-Glazed Bok Choy with Sriracha Mayo and Ginger-Infused Jasmine Rice
description: In this dish, salmon is pan-fried to a crispy finish and bok choy is featured and drizzled with a sweet soy glaze. Served with ginger-infused rice and light and aromatic sriracha mayo, this Japanese inspired meal is an ideal weeknight supper!
